quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Anthu okhulupirira ndiwo opambana
  23,2,Iwo amene amadzichepetsa akamapemphera
  23,3,Ndi iwo amene amalewa nkhani zabodza
  23,4,Ndipo amapereka zaulere kwa anthu osauka
  23,5,Ndi iwo amene amadziteteza ku chiwerewere
  23,6,"Kupatula kwa akazi awo kapena akapolo awo akazi, chifukwa iwo sangadzudzulidwe"
  23,7,Koma amene angafune zina pamwamba pa zimene tawaloleza anthu otere ndi ochimwa
  23,8,Amene amakwaniritsa malonjezo ndi mapangano awo
  23,9,Ndi iwo amene amasunga mapemphero awo
  23,10,Amenewa ndithudi ndiwo amene adzalowa
  23,11,Iwo adzalowa ku Paradiso ya pamwamba ndipo adzakhalamo mpaka kalekale
  23,12,Ndithudi Ife tidapanga munthu kuchokera ku dothi labwino
  23,13,Titatero tidamukonza iye kukhala dontho la umuna m’malo otetezedwa mu msana
  23,14,"dontho la umunali tidalipanga kukhala dontho la magazi ndipo dontho lamagazili tidalipanga kukhala m’bulu wa mnofu. Ndipo mnofu umenewu tidaukonza kukhala mafupa ndipo tidakuta mafupa ndi mnofu. Kotero tidamupanga iye kukhala chilengedwe china. odalitsa akhale Mulungu, Namalenga wabwino kwambiri mwa onse"
  23,15,Ndipo pambuyo pake inu nonse mudzafa
  23,16,Ndipo mudzapatsidwanso moyo patsiku la kuuka kwa akufa
  23,17,Ife tidalenga miyamba isanu ndi iwiri pamwamba panu ndipo kwa zolengedwa zathu. Ndipo Ife sitikhala osalabadira ayi
  23,18,Ife timatumiza madzi kuchokera kumwamba m’muyeso wokwana ndipo timawalowetsa pansi pa nthaka. Ndipo Ife tili ndi mphamvu yowachotsa madziwo
  23,19,"Ndipo Ife timakutulutsirani mmenemo minda ya tende ndi mphesa, m’mene muli zipatso zanu zambiri zimene zina mwa izo mumadya"
  23,20,"Mtengo umene umamera pa phiri la Sinai, umapereka mafuta ndiponso ndiwo kwa anthu"
  23,21,M’nyama namonso muli chizindikiro choonetsa mphamvu zathu. Inu timakumwetsani zimene zili m’mimba mwake ndipo mumadya nyama yake ndiponso mumapeza phindu lambiri
  23,22,"Ndipo pa izo ndi m’zombo zimene zimayenda pa nyanja, inu mumanyamulidwa"
  23,23,"Tidamutumiza Nowa kwa anthu ake ndipo iye adati, “Tumikirani Mulungu anthu anga chifukwa mulibe mulungu wina koma Iye yekha. Kodi simungamuope Iye?”"
  23,24,"Akuluakulu osakhulupirira a anthu ake adati, “Munthu uyu ndi wolingana ndi inu, iye ali kungodziyenereza kuti ndi wopambana pakati panu.” Mulungu akadafuna, akadatumiza angelo. Ndiponso zinthu za mtundu uwu sitidamvepo kuchokera kwa makolo athu akalekale"
  23,25,"Ndithudi ameneyu ndi wopenga, ndipo mumuyang’anire pa kanthawi.”"
  23,26,"Iye adati, “Ambuye! Ndithandizeni ine chifukwa iwo ali kundikana.”"
  23,27,"Ife tidavumbulutsa chifuniro chathu kwa iye ponena kuti, “Khoma chombo chimene Ife tidzayang’anira molingana ndi chilangizo chathu. Pamene chiweruzo chathu chidza ndipo madzi asefukira kuchokera ku ng’anjo, utenge zolengedwa ziwiriziwiri, zazimuna ndi zazikazi ndiponso kuchokera kwa iwo a m’nyumba mwako kupatula okhawo amene adanenedwa kuti adzaonongeka. Usandipemphe kuti ndipulumutse iwo amene adachita zoipa chifukwa iwo adzamizidwa.”"
  23,28,"Ndipo pamene iwe ndi iwo amene akutsata iwe mulowa m’chombo, nena, “Kuyamikidwa kukhale kwa Mulungu amene watipulumutsa ife kuchoka ku mtundu wa anthu oipa.”"
  23,29,"Ndipo nena: “Ambuye wanga! Ndithandizeni kuti ndikafike pamalo podalitsika chifukwa Inu ndinu wabwino wa onse amene amafikitsa pamalo okocheza.”"
  23,30,Ndithudi mu zimenezi muli zizindikiro zooneka. Ndithudi Ife timawaika anthu m’mayesero
  23,31,Potero Ife tidapanga mtundu wa anthu a tsopano pambuyo pawo
  23,32,"Ndipo tidatumiza kwa iwo Mtumwi wa mtundu wawo amene adati, “Tumikirani Mulungu chifukwa inu mulibe mulungu wina koma Iye yekha. Kodi simungamuope Mulungu?”"
  23,33,"Koma akuluakulu a anthu osakhulupirira a anthu ake, amene adakana za moyo umene uli nkudza ndi amene tidawapatsa zinthu zabwino za m’moyo uno adati, “Munthu uyu ndi munthu monga inu nomwe amene akudya zimene mumadya inu ndi kumwa zimene inu mumamwa.”"
  23,34,"“Ngati inu mumvera munthu wonga inu nomwe, ndithudi, inu mudzatayika.”"
  23,35,“Kodi iye ali kukuopsezani kuti pamene inu mutafa ndi kusanduka dothi ndi mafupa mudzadzuka ndi kukhalanso ndi moyo?”